languages.text:
Cybermastiff's attacks force their targets to make pass a Toughness test or become immobilized. If they pass they become slowed instead.
Each successfull hit also inflicts {g|f:b4abe53c3f894c1fb2c58d137c806279}Chewed{/g}.
